      "fields": {
        "entryTitle": "META - L1 - About this site",
        "heading": "About Gareth de Walters",
        "standfirst": "Summary",
        "body": {
          "nodeType": "document",
          "data": {},
          "content": [
            {
              "nodeType": "heading-2",
              "data": {},
              "content": [
                {
                  "nodeType": "text",
                  "value": "I make websites",
                  "marks": [],
                  "data": {}
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "nodeType": "paragraph",
              "data": {},
              "content": [
                {
                  "nodeType": "text",
                  "value": "I'm an Auckland-based website manager. I've produced websites and digtal experiences for the British Film Institute, the University of Auckland, Auckland War Memorial Museum, Vodafone, Heart Foundation and Chorus.",
                  "marks": [],
                  "data": {}
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "nodeType": "paragraph",
              "data": {},
              "content": [
                {
                  "nodeType": "text",
                  "value": "This is my personal site where I write about the web, genealogy, history, music, and food.",
                  "marks": [],
                  "data": {}
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "nodeType": "heading-2",
              "data": {},
              "content": [
                {
                  "nodeType": "text",
                  "value": "Work experience",
                  "marks": [],
                  "data": {}
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "nodeType": "paragraph",
              "data": {},
              "content": [
                {
                  "nodeType": "text",
                  "value": "I orginally trained to be an archaelogist, but after moving to England in investigate a masters in forensic archaeolgy I started working for the webhost Rapidsite, and have worked in the world of web ever since.",
                  "marks": [],
                  "data": {}
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "nodeType": "paragraph",
              "data": {},
              "content": [
                {
                  "nodeType": "text",
                  "value": "Rapidsite was bought out by Verio/NTT, and after that I joined the web team and the amazing marketing and eductaion teams at the British Film Institute. Since then I've worked for public service and private organisations. I'm now the Websites Lead at Chorus where I work between marketing and technology teams to deliver a variety of digital experiences and channels.",
                  "marks": [],
                  "data": {}
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "nodeType": "paragraph",
              "data": {},
              "content": [
                {
                  "nodeType": "text",
                  "value": "You can read more about my experience on ",
                  "marks": [],
                  "data": {}
                },
                {
                  "nodeType": "hyperlink",
                  "data": {
                    "uri": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gdewalters/"
                  },
                  "content": [
