              "content": [
                {
                  "nodeType": "text",
                  "value": "The site logo incorporates the gules (red) three chevronels argent (silvery white) from the flag of Glamorgan (yn Gymraeg: Baner Morgannwg). That design was in turn taken from the arms of Iestyn ap Gwrgant, the last independent ruler of Glamorgan – the region where many of my Welsh family comes from.",
